Class ChemicalPropertiesTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataTableIO
      • ChemicalPropertiesTable

  • public class ChemicalPropertiesTable
extends DataTableIO
    A table for chemical properties with unique methods for getting units and species names.

      Constructor and Description
      ChemicalPropertiesTable()
      Prompts the user to select a CSV file containing the data table.

      Reads in the table at the path provided.

    • Method Detail

      • extractHeadings

        public java.lang.String[][] extractHeadings()
        Gets the first two rows of the table (Headings and units) and returns them as columns. It's better to return a vertical array as it prints to the console much nicer.
        Returns:
        a 2D array containing the headings and their associated units as columns

      • extractIdentities

        public java.lang.String[][] extractIdentities()
        Gets the species name and ID number columns and returns them as columns. It's better to return a vertical array as it prints to the console much nicer.
        Returns:
        a 2D array containing the species name and ID number
